OL,3,CHundreds of firefighters battle Spain
OL,4,Cwildfire that killed at least 12
OL,6,FHundreds of firefighters backed by
OL,7,Fhelicopters and fixed-wing aircraft
OL,8,Fstruggled on Saturday to contain one
OL,9,Fof Spain's deadliest wildfires that
OL,10,Ferupted earlier this week and killed
OL,11,Fat least 12 people, including four
OL,12,FBritish citizens.
OL,14,FThe blazes, which also lashed France
OL,15,Fthis week, came as parts of Western
OL,16,FEurope are facing their third heat
OL,17,Fwave in six weeks.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
