OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783900129
OL,3,CHundreds of firefighters battle Spain
OL,4,Cwildfire that killed at least 12
OL,6,FEurope is the world's fastest-warming
OL,7,Fcontinent, with temperatures
OL,8,Fincreasing twice as fast as the global
OL,9,Faverage since the 1980s, according to
OL,10,Fthe European Union's Copernicus
OL,11,FClimate Change Service.
OL,13,FIn Spain's Andalusia, a combination of
OL,14,Flight winds and high humidity is
OL,15,Fhelping crews, but the sheer size of
OL,16,Fthe fire still poses challenges,
OL,17,FAntonio Sanz, head of the region's
OL,18,Femergency services, said.
OL,20,FThe fire has so far scorched some 25
OL,21,Fsquare miles of forest and farmland.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
