OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783900129
OL,3,CHundreds of firefighters battle Spain
OL,4,Cwildfire that killed at least 12
OL,6,FSanz said fire crews carried out
OL,7,Fcontrolled burns overnight around the
OL,8,Fperimeter of the fire, which broke out
OL,9,Flate on Thursday in a semi-arid area
OL,10,Fnear the Sierra de Los Filabres
OL,11,Fmountains in Almeria province.
OL,13,FFavourable weather conditions were
OL,14,Fexpected into Sunday, which could help
OL,15,Ffirefighting efforts, Spain's official
OL,16,FEFE news agency reported. Justice
OL,17,FMinister Felix Bolanos said nearly all
OL,18,Fhomes on the fire front's perimeter
OL,19,Fwere undamaged.
