OL,3,CHundreds of firefighters battle Spain
OL,4,Cwildfire that killed at least 12
OL,6,FMost of the victims, who are believed
OL,7,Fto be foreign nationals, died after
OL,8,Fignoring shelter-in-place
OL,9,Finstructions, authorities said. Seven
OL,10,Fpeople died while on foot after
OL,11,Fabandoning their cars.
OL,13,FFour of the dead were believed to be
OL,14,FBritish because the steering wheel of
OL,15,Ftheir burned-out car was on the right
OL,16,Fside, regional authorities said.
OL,18,FSanz said on Saturday that authorities
OL,19,Fhad completed autopsies and DNA
OL,20,Fsamples were collected to identify
OL,21,Fthem.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
