OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783900129
OL,3,CHundreds of firefighters battle Spain
OL,4,Cwildfire that killed at least 12
OL,6,FSpain's Foreign Minister Jose Manuel
OL,7,FAlbares has spoken with his
OL,8,Fcounterparts from the UK Belgium,
OL,9,FCanada and the Netherlands about the
OL,10,Ffire, EFE reported. Almeria is home to
OL,11,Fone of the largest communities of
OL,12,Fforeign nationals in Andalusia.
OL,14,FAuthorities proactively evacuated
OL,15,F1,448 people from some 11 areas.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
