OL,3,CHundreds of firefighters battle Spain
OL,4,Cwildfire that killed at least 12
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Spanish authorities
OL,7,Farrested two people for ignoring
OL,8,Fevacuation orders and returning to a
OL,9,Fhigh-risk area, according to EFE.
OL,10,FAuthorities are still combing through
OL,11,Fthe Bedar area in search for any
OL,12,Fvictims.
