OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F318A1783900129
OL,3,CHundreds of firefighters battle Spain
OL,4,Cwildfire that killed at least 12
OL,6,FSpain has battled frequent and severe
OL,7,Fheat waves in recent years, with
OL,8,Ftemperatures often exceeding 40C.
OL,9,FWind, high temperatures and little
OL,10,Frainfall help small wildfires grow
OL,11,Finto unchecked blazes.
OL,13,FBolanos, the justice minister, on
OL,14,FSaturday attributed the ferocity of
OL,15,Fthe Almeira wildfire to a "climate
OL,16,Femergency." He said the fire, at its
OL,17,Fmost intense, advanced as fast as 100
OL,18,Fmeters per minute (328 feet per
OL,19,Fminute.)
