OL,3,CHundreds of firefighters battle Spain
OL,4,Cwildfire that killed at least 12
OL,6,FSpain's Meteorological Agency warned
OL,7,Fthat the wildfire risk over the
OL,8,Fweekend will remain very high.
OL,10,FIn June, Spain experienced several
OL,11,Fdays of record-setting heat, with over
OL,12,F1,000 excess deaths. Globally, 2025
OL,13,Fwas the third-hottest year on record,
OL,14,Fbringing several intense heat waves
OL,15,Facross Europe.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/9
