OL,3,CHundreds of firefighters battle Spain
OL,4,Cwildfire that killed at least 12
OL,6,FSeveral wildfires remained active
OL,7,Facross France on Saturday as
OL,8,Ftemperatures soared. Interior Minister
OL,9,FLaurent Nunez said that 32 people have
OL,10,Fbeen arrested across the country since
OL,11,Fthe beginning of the summer in
OL,12,Fconnection with wildfires.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/9
